<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="specialise-vi">specialise <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'speʃəlaɪz/    美 /'speʃəlaɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>专门研究；专门从事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He decided to <strong>specialize in</strong> economics when in college.
他决定大学期间专攻经济学。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That shop <strong>specializes in</strong> foreign magazines.
那家商店专营外国杂志。</p></div></div>